<Author>TFlyer
<Content>Great Find in Berlin! I had the lowest category room in the hotel but the room was nicely appointed (room safe, TV, WIFI, new furnishings, art and design with a modern, hip, flair), with a spacious bathroom, large armoire - all spotlessly clean and refreshed daily. The (price included) breakfast buffet was lavish with hot and cold items, endless coffee and fresh fruit. The location is excellent next to the Tiergarten S-Bahn so easy to get anywhere including to/from Tegel for 2 euros! Also right on a bike/wlaking path up and down the Spree River so it is perfect for quiet strolls, biking or jogs. The hotel provides free WIFI plus a PC station for those without a computer. The staff gladly researched information if they didn't happen to know it. I couldn't have been more pleased. Superb value for money. 
